{"tid":313902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[憤入] 幫小強消暑","createTime":"2017-07-08T17:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T18:00:02.000Z","uid":11515,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49612f8c50436630eb121fc83a99418670dce519","tid":313902,"uid":11515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T17:23:00.000Z","msg":"剛剛入廚房發現有隻強閃閃縮縮<br />\n一開燈即刻去黑暗既地方唔郁<br />\n以為我就搵唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/010922_18e5b6f3bedb2dca087700323e5e698b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F010922_18e5b6f3bedb2dca087700323e5e698b.jpg&h=55a99496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見佢企左係度，我已經諗緊點收拾佢<br />\n屋企無咩滅蟲工具，入房睇下有咩好洗好用<br />\n見到呢支野<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/011517_3e8b7315ec3ec4b6de98514293bd7480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F011517_3e8b7315ec3ec4b6de98514293bd7480.jpg&h=e627a744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢支野如果各位巴絲有用過，<br />\n就知噴少少落衫已經好勁好清涼<br />\n如果直接落皮膚一定勁&quot;乸&quot;<br />\n咁我開始同佢搏鬥<br />\n我追住佢係咁噴<br />\n噴左大約30秒，噴到我都有少少乸眼<br />\n佢就開始慢慢喪失行動力，反肚，然後最後掙扎<br />\n最後係彊左<br />\n附上遺照一張<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/012248_9ca59f59e90e5da0e0e074c19040fe53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F012248_9ca59f59e90e5da0e0e074c19040fe53.jpg&h=99d6e7de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji